 ports. Exact due date depends on each report's operating month\, not the c
 alendar month of this reminder - adjust to your program's cycle:\n- FNS-10
  (School Program Operations) - Items 5-9 - Submit via FPRS\n- FNS-44 (CACF
 P Report) - Parts A & E monthly\; Part D is 90-day only - Submit via FPRS\
 n- FNS-418 (Summer Food Service Program Report) - Part A\, during operatin
 g months - Submit via FPRS\nRule: 'Estimated' data is due 30 days after th
 e report month ends\; 'Actual' data is due 90 days after the report month 
 ends.
